api_list.name: Get SubRegions
api_list.description: Get list of sub regions in the world
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://geography4.p.rapidapi.com/apis/geography/v1/subregion"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "geography4.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
